《芝加哥医学》中反复扮演角色。她在 ABC 警匪剧《新秀》中担任主演。","name":"梅基亚·考克斯","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"מקיה קוקס","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Мекиа Кокс","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"梅基亞·考克斯（Mekia Cox）是一位女演員，歌手和舞者。她是邁克爾·傑克遜演唱會系列《這就是它》和相關電影邁克爾·傑克遜的《這就是它》的舞者。\n\n她曾在《90210》、《案內人》、《蒂亞娜公主往事》、《幾乎是人類》、《牧師》、《秘密與謊言》和《芝加哥醫學》中反覆扮演角色。她在 ABC 警匪劇《新秀》中擔任主演。","name":"梅姬婭·考克斯","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Mekia Cox (18 de noviembre de 1981) es una actriz y bailarina estadounidense, conocida por sus papeles de Sasha en el drama de CW 90210, la Dra. Robin Charles en el drama médico de NBC Chicago Med y la detective Nyla Harper en el drama policial de ABC The Rookie.","name":"","primary":false}}]}},"person_4497686_translations":{"at":1774211404451,"data":{"id":4497686,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Tânia Maria (born January 19, 1947) is a Brazilian actress, craftswoman and dressmaker, known for Bacurau (2019) and The Secret Agent (2025).","name":"Tânia Maria","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"Tânia Maria é uma atriz, artesã e costureira brasileira, conhecida por Bacurau (2019) e O Agente Secreto (2025).","name":"Tânia Maria","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Таня Мария","primary":false}}]}},"person_5439502_translations":{"at":1774211411484,"data":{"id":5439502,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Natthanich